text_raw:
EXPLANATORY NOTE 

(This note is not part of the Instrument and does not purport to be a legal 
interpretation) 

This Order appoints the 21st day of October 2020 as the date on which the 
provisions of Part 1 and section 4 of the CervicalCheck Tribunal Act 2019 
come into operation. 

This Order appoints the 27th day of October 2020 as the date on which the 
provisions of sections 5 to 10 of Chapter 1 of Part 2, Chapters 2, 3, 4, 6 and 7 
of Part 2, and Part 3 of the CervicalCheck Tribunal Act 2019 come into 
operation.
